#include "Engine.hpp"

// A dummy example 
int main() {
    // Create pixels buffer
    const auto pixels = std::make_unique(new uint8_t[1024*1024*3]);
    fillData(*pixels, "path/to/texture.png");

    // Create a texture out of the pixels
    Engine::Graphics::Texture2D texture(1024, 1024, *data);

    // Done
    return 0;
}
